name: MLODZIPROAKTYWNI POLSKA
goal: MLODZIPROAKTYWNI POLSKA is a Polish foundation devoted to the promotion of leadership, coaching, personal development, entrepreneurship. We organize trainings sessions, and conferences helping young people to enter the labor market or to start their own business.
euInitiatives: Education and Training 2020, Europe 2020, Horizon 2020, Erasmus+, proceeding in the European Parliament's Committee on Youth and Culture (CULT)
